### 3.7 Module 7: REST API

**Priority:** P1 (Important - MVP)  
**Target:** Month 3

#### Features:

**F7.1 API Authentication**

- JWT token-based authentication
- API key generation per tenant
- Token expiration (24 hours)
- Token refresh endpoint

**F7.2 Core Endpoints (MVP)**

**Suppliers:**

- GET /api/v1/suppliers (list with pagination, filters)
- GET /api/v1/suppliers/{id} (single supplier)
- POST /api/v1/suppliers (create)
- PUT /api/v1/suppliers/{id} (update)
- DELETE /api/v1/suppliers/{id} (soft delete)

**Evaluations:**

- GET /api/v1/evaluations (list)
- GET /api/v1/evaluations/{id}
- POST /api/v1/evaluations (create)
- PUT /api/v1/evaluations/{id}

**Complaints:**

- GET /api/v1/complaints (list)
- GET /api/v1/complaints/{id}
- POST /api/v1/complaints (create)
- PUT /api/v1/complaints/{id}
- PUT /api/v1/complaints/{id}/status (update status)

**Qualifications:**

- GET /api/v1/qualifications (list)
- GET /api/v1/qualifications/{id}
- POST /api/v1/qualifications (create)
- PUT /api/v1/qualifications/{id}/approve (approve/reject)

**F7.3 API Documentation**

- OpenAPI 3.0 specification
- Interactive API documentation (Swagger UI)
- Code examples in curl, JavaScript, Python
- Authentication guide
- Rate limiting documentation

**F7.4 API Rate Limiting**

- 1000 requests per hour per tenant (MVP)
- 429 response when exceeded
- Rate limit headers in response

**F7.5 Webhooks (Phase 2)**

- Out of scope for MVP

