## 4. User Stories & Acceptance Criteria

### 4.1 Tenant & User Management

#### **US-1.1: User Login**

**As a** registered user  
**I want to** log in to Supplex using my email and password  
**So that** I can access my company's supplier data securely

**Acceptance Criteria:**

- [ ] Login page displays email and password fields
- [ ] Valid credentials redirect to dashboard
- [ ] Invalid credentials show error message "Invalid email or password"
- [ ] After 5 failed attempts, account is locked for 15 minutes
- [ ] "Remember me" checkbox keeps session active for 30 days
- [ ] Successful login creates JWT token with tenant_id and role claims
- [ ] Session expires after 8 hours of inactivity

**Priority:** P0  
**Estimate:** 3 story points

---

#### **US-1.2: Password Reset**

**As a** user who forgot my password  
**I want to** reset it via email  
**So that** I can regain access to my account

**Acceptance Criteria:**

- [ ] "Forgot password?" link on login page
- [ ] Enter email, receive reset link within 2 minutes
- [ ] Reset link expires after 1 hour
- [ ] Reset page requires new password (min 8 chars, 1 uppercase, 1 number)
- [ ] Password successfully changed, redirect to login
- [ ] Old password no longer works
- [ ] Email notification sent on successful password change

**Priority:** P0  
**Estimate:** 3 story points

---

#### **US-1.3: Add New User**

**As an** Admin  
**I want to** add new users to my tenant  
**So that** my team members can access the system

**Acceptance Criteria:**

- [ ] Admin navigates to Settings > Users > Add User
- [ ] Form requires: first name, last name, email, role
- [ ] Email must be unique within tenant
- [ ] Available roles: Admin, Procurement, Quality, Viewer
- [ ] User receives invitation email with setup link
- [ ] Invitation link expires after 7 days
- [ ] New user sets password on first login
- [ ] User appears in user list after setup

**Priority:** P0  
**Estimate:** 5 story points

---

### 4.2 Supplier Master Data

#### **US-2.1: Create New Supplier**

**As a** Procurement user  
**I want to** create a new supplier profile  
**So that** I can track their information and performance

**Acceptance Criteria:**

- [ ] Navigate to Suppliers > Add New Supplier
- [ ] Required fields: Supplier name, status
- [ ] Optional fields: All contact info, certifications, financial info
- [ ] Supplier code auto-generated in format: SUP-YYYY-0001
- [ ] Can manually override supplier code
- [ ] Duplicate name warning (not blocking)
- [ ] Status defaults to "Prospect"
- [ ] Success message displayed on save
- [ ] Supplier appears in supplier list immediately

**Priority:** P0  
**Estimate:** 5 story points

---

#### **US-2.2: View Supplier Details**

**As a** user  
**I want to** view complete supplier information  
**So that** I can understand their capabilities and status

**Acceptance Criteria:**

- [ ] Click supplier name from list to view details
- [ ] All supplier fields displayed in organized sections
- [ ] Contact information section with all contacts
- [ ] Certifications table with expiry dates highlighted if < 30 days
- [ ] Documents list with download buttons
- [ ] Activity history showing recent evaluations, complaints, changes
- [ ] Quick actions: Edit, Evaluate, Report Complaint
- [ ] Breadcrumb navigation: Home > Suppliers > [Supplier Name]

**Priority:** P0  
**Estimate:** 5 story points

---

#### **US-2.3: Upload Supplier Document**

**As a** Procurement or Quality user  
**I want to** upload documents for a supplier  
**So that** I can keep certifications and contracts organized

**Acceptance Criteria:**

- [ ] On supplier detail page, Documents section with "Upload" button
- [ ] Drag-and-drop or file browser upload
- [ ] Supported formats: PDF, DOC, DOCX, XLS, XLSX, JPG, PNG
- [ ] Max file size: 25MB per file
- [ ] Required fields: Document type, document name
- [ ] Optional: Expiry date
- [ ] Document appears in list immediately after upload
- [ ] File stored in Supabase Storage with tenant isolation
- [ ] Document URL accessible only to tenant users

**Priority:** P0  
**Estimate:** 5 story points

---

#### **US-2.4: Search Suppliers**

**As a** user  
**I want to** search for suppliers by name or code  
**So that** I can quickly find specific suppliers

**Acceptance Criteria:**

- [ ] Search box at top of supplier list page
- [ ] Search starts after typing 2+ characters
- [ ] Searches across: supplier name, supplier code, contact names
- [ ] Results update in real-time (debounced 300ms)
- [ ] No results shows "No suppliers found matching '[query]'"
- [ ] Clear search button (X icon)
- [ ] Search persists through pagination

**Priority:** P0  
**Estimate:** 3 story points

---

#### **US-2.5: Filter Suppliers**

**As a** user  
**I want to** filter suppliers by status, category, and risk level  
**So that** I can focus on specific supplier segments

**Acceptance Criteria:**

- [ ] Filter panel on left side of supplier list
- [ ] Filter by status: checkboxes for Prospect, Qualified, Approved, Blocked
- [ ] Filter by category: dropdown with all categories
- [ ] Filter by risk level: checkboxes for Low, Medium, High, Critical
- [ ] Filter by certification expiry: "Expiring soon" (< 30 days), "Expired"
- [ ] Multiple filters combine with AND logic
- [ ] Active filters shown as tags above list
- [ ] Clear all filters button
- [ ] Filtered count shown: "Showing X of Y suppliers"

**Priority:** P1  
**Estimate:** 5 story points

