## 13. Appendix

### 13.1 Glossary

**CAPA:** Corrective and Preventive Actions - steps taken to eliminate the causes of detected non-conformities

**ERP:** Enterprise Resource Planning - business process management software

**KPI:** Key Performance Indicator - measurable value demonstrating effectiveness

**MVP:** Minimum Viable Product - product with minimum features to satisfy early customers

**NPS:** Net Promoter Score - metric for measuring customer loyalty (-100 to +100)

**P0/P1/P2:** Priority levels (P0 = Critical, P1 = High, P2 = Medium)

**RLS:** Row-Level Security - database security feature that restricts row access

**SLA:** Service Level Agreement - commitment between service provider and customer

**WCAG:** Web Content Accessibility Guidelines - accessibility recommendations

